data.description: Look at this Gem !  This Beautiful Ranch home is now available. This stunning 3 bedroom 2 bath home has it all. Built in 2015 this home is move in ready.  1.45 acres  with a big fenced backyard. Attached 2 car garage. The upgrades to this home feature two completely remodeled bath rooms with fixtures.  New ac in 2022 and a new roof in 2017. New water softener  along with new sump pump and ejector pump. Newer energy efficient furnace.  Spacious covered front porch with a big attached walkout deck to enjoy sunsets.  Big downstairs  living area with shower and bathroom. Come see everything this beautiful home has to offer. Schedule your showing today
